<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT2">
<l>tēruṅkā ṟēva ṉoruvaṉē yeṉṟuraippa</l>
<l>rāru maṟiyā ravaṉperumai yōrum</l>
<l>poruḷmuṭivu mittaṉaiyē yettavamcey tārkku</l>
<l>maruḷmuṭiva tāḻiyāṉ pāl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While examining, they say there is but one god.</l>
<l>Nobody knows His greatness.</l>
<l>This much is the conclusion of the examined meaning.</l>
<l>Grace appears from Him with the discus</l>
<l rend="indent">for those who performed any [kind of] penance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
